10:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>And one last powerful attribute</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>that comedy has as communication</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637000' id='t-637000'>is that it's inherently viral.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639000' id='t-639000'>People can't wait</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641000' id='t-641000'>to pass along that new great joke.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='643000' id='t-643000'>And this isn't some new phenomenon of our wired world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='646000' id='t-646000'>Comedy has been crossing country</span>
