<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='744000' id='t-744000'>So we started talking about climate change.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='747000' id='t-747000'>And it turned out that Joel and I</span>
